title: Tezos Filipinos
description:
In line with the celebration of National Language Month, this event aims to build awareness in contributing digital footprint of history, arts and culture in the Philippines.
Open to all Filipino artists, mint your artwork with a least one Filipino word • 88 editions • swap at 0.8 XTZ • burn all remaining edition on september 1.
Use tag tezosfilipinos at mint to appear on this event page.
